On Tuesday, the market retreated to this week's lowest level of
433.8 points, with banking stocks sliding to considerably lower
levels.
</P>
<P>
The total volume of transactions this week amounted to 8.2
million Cyprus pounds (about 16.4 million U.S. dollars), from
10.5 million pounds (about 21 million dollars) the week before.
</P>
