<TEXT>
<P>
BUENOS AIRES, May 21 (Xinhua) -- The Argentine National
Airports Regulatory System Organization (Orsna) Thursday signed an
agreement on technical assistance with the U.S. Trade and
Development Program (TDP).
</P>
<P>
